{"tid":2138904,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"35+已超額完成 - 戴耀廷","createTime":"2020-08-04T02:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T08:23:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":41,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"07b482b099f6625436b935471e6ff6a1f22bcf26","tid":2138904,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/QD5UG6QXVFRDWMO4SJXBPKHUOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FQD5UG6QXVFRDWMO4SJXBPKHUOQ%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O1KEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=50674a38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FQD5UG6QXVFRDWMO4SJXBPKHUOQ%2F&h=13de0702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/QD5UG6QXVFRDWMO4SJXBPKHUOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n35+已超額完成 - 戴耀廷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LrhkkRaVYKgZEKU0o9gbBvIJYIw=/1587x1000/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6BSFU5E7LE3IWXCZCCVTY6RPIE.gifA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLrhkkRaVYKgZEKU0o9gbBvIJYIw%3D%2F1587x1000%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6BSFU5E7LE3IWXCZCCVTY6RPIE.gifA&h=5daf323b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥宣佈押後立法會。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主派在7月舉行的初選，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n即使民主派在地區直選和。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中共直接助推達標<br />\n<br />\n而且，真的做到35＋，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會已直接為。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n35＋終極目標要透過。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n雖然選舉主任以各種理由包括反對國安法和否決《財政預算案》，取消了12位民主派參選人的參選資格，但押後選舉的表面理由是抗疫。既是因疫情而沒有了選舉，那些針對民主派35＋違反國安法的指控，就再難成立，被取消資格的人下年9月仍可參選。因此，民主派通過一次初選，令中共及特區政權完全亂了陣腳，35＋的目標亦已超額完成。中共及特區政權要任意扭曲法律才能應對35＋，進一步暴露出它們的專制本質，撕破法律「畫皮」，會令更多人走到政權的對立面，使統治成本進一步加重，可說是35＋額外的「政治花紅」。<br />\n<br />\n下年9月會否有。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在未來一年，抗爭力量更重要做的，是重整力量，紮穩已建立起的社區網絡，鞏固得來不易的團結，並為有可能快要出現的巨變，做好所有準備。<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷"},{"pid":"6b83dbd9f96b6df4afc4a8b01890b855ce65d5d4","tid":2138904,"uid":76609,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"PR公司：呀Q精神"},{"pid":"e9fcdf42fef79b8b629bedb63b51d16fa46a6dfe","tid":2138904,"uid":64131,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/04/111753_0725f859cb851a47888cc8e8f655d41a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F04%2F111753_0725f859cb851a47888cc8e8f655d41a.jpg&h=43fb4686&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40f91892b2b4f325006b67ee4ad21fe2f5a54e75","tid":2138904,"uid":62837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:08:02.000Z","msg":"計中計?"},{"pid":"ce409896aababc1517ceffee36ce2e749831e3c5","tid":2138904,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:08:35.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"8447d3ac82c3180db7e1689d71dfc53bc432c5e1","tid":2138904,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"未選先贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c47e03f26e1ce91f9519ece60f7a52168200d9c","tid":2138904,"uid":201464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:10:31.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n失敗就唔駛dq/延期<br />\n直接舉行選舉"},{"pid":"160441cd4f956caca5e9e68b1d92e7bf011aa6b1","tid":2138904,"uid":143343,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a59ad5e60f72a4194411d67a071a7544ef08a8a","tid":2138904,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:11:58.000Z","msg":"戴生輸到痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f936af93f6dfe406b46c5848c0611e995cb85a3","tid":2138904,"uid":128923,"li