dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf6d3676cefe02cb13f4f324e841f39b01b9417","tid":2138904,"uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:21:54.000Z","msg":"中共現在已做了最愚蠢的決定，也不用做甚麼游說工作，國際社會的制裁陸續有來，35＋的歷史任務因而也完成了。"},{"pid":"a1fa0718607197f94c4514583c951c88418f5c8b","tid":2138904,"uid":270418,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:21:55.000Z","msg":"雖然話 35+呢樣野 最終會唔會真係做到無人知<br />\n<br />\n有無效 都無人知<br />\n<br />\n但支共打橫黎 乜都驚 就係人都知<br />\n<br />\n依家DQ 加 延期 呢啲唔合理嘅野一次過做曬<br />\n<br />\n都唔知算唔算意外收穫<br />\n<br />\n另一方面嘅加速成功 支共再出醜於國際"},{"pid":"1cf6203738d5b69627e0aba0e0415f31719ba23d","tid":2138904,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"在未來一年，中共必會再加大打壓的力度，我們必須咬緊牙關捱過去。"},{"pid":"7e36d01b6b6102a0ecac912c2c9c4e4b48ecca37","tid":2138904,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b83dbd9f96b6df4afc4a8b01890b855ce65d5d4","tid":2138904,"uid":76609,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:00:21.000Z","msg":"PR公司：呀Q精神"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:25:30.000Z","msg":"美佢地連美國政府既說話，都話係9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a938c26fdce11be041bd10daae1de3d680b4880","tid":2138904,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"其實，球已到中共的場中去，抗爭力量反不用急於在接着的階段再做些甚麼對抗行動，因能做的都已做了。"}]}